Class YieldCurve

Namespace
ECBFinanceAPI.Loaders.YieldCurves.Models
Assembly
ECBFinanceAPI.dll

Represents a yield curve composed of a collection of YieldCurveQuote items. The curve provides access to the underlying quotes, an indexer for retrieving yields by Maturity, and optional fitted NelsonSiegelSvenssonParameters describing the curve shape.

public class YieldCurve : IEnumerable<YieldCurveQuote>, IEnumerable
